A videogame inspired by Bitcoin culture and the Bitcoin-sovereign nation of El Salvador

Play the Adventure

Journey to El Salvador as Hero, a new bitcoiner who is determined to join the fight for Bitcoin adoption. Navigate through iconic locations like Bitcoin Beach and volcanic landscapes, making your way to the bank's doorstep.

Help President Bukele and fellow bitcoiners overcome challenges from poocoiners, bears, and traditional banking systems. This classic Game Boy adventure combines retro gaming nostalgia with the revolutionary spirit of Bitcoin culture.

Authentic Game Boy platformer experience
Explore real El Salvador Bitcoin locations
Collect 21 hidden Bitcoin throughout your journey
Meet iconic Bitcoin personalities and characters
